'''安宁阿敏'''（'''Amrin Amin''' ）是一名新加坡政治家，[[2015年新加坡大選|2015年大選]]首次代表[[人民行動黨|人民行動黨]]出選並勝出。他是一位律师。<ref name="pap">{{cite web|url=https://www.pap.org.sg/Amrin_Amin/Article|title=People's Action Party|publisher=pap.org.sg|accessdate=2015-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208165145/https://www.pap.org.sg/Amrin_Amin/Article|archive-date=2015-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="mustsharenews">{{cite web|url=http://mustsharenews.com/pap-amrin-amin-interview/|title=[EXCLUSIVE]: PAP’s Sembawang GRC Candidate Amrin Amin Speaks With MustShareNews - MustShareNews.com|publisher=mustsharenews.com|accessdate=2015-08-30|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204080838/https://mustsharenews.com/pap-amrin-amin-interview/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="mustsharenews2">{{cite web|url=http://mustsharenews.com/new-candidates-sg-ge/|title=20 Potential Candidates To Look Out For In The Coming General Elections - MustShareNews.com|publisher=mustsharenews.com|accessdate=2015-08-30|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024120739/https://mustsharenews.com/new-candidates-sg-ge/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="asiaone">{{cite web|url=http://news.asiaone.com/news/singapore/lawyer-potential-pap-candidate|title=Lawyer a potential PAP candidate, AsiaOne Singapore News|publisher=news.asiaone.com|accessdate=2015-08-30|archive-date=2016-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213142758/http://news.asiaone.com/news/singapore/lawyer-potential-pap-candidate|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==教育==
先後就讀[[德明政府中學|德明政府中學]]和[[淡滨尼初级学院|淡滨尼初级学院]]，後來分別於[[新加坡國立大學|新加坡國立大學]]和[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]取得法學士和法學碩士<ref name="pap2">{{cite web|url=https://www.pap.org.sg/upload/item/2015Candidate/Amrin%20Amin_CV_Statement.pdf|date=13 August 2015|author=Lilian NG (MOH)|title=AMRIN AMIN 安宁阿敏|accessdate=2015-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112181734/https://www.pap.org.sg/upload/item/2015Candidate/Amrin%20Amin_CV_Statement.pdf|archive-date=2016-01-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==政治生涯==
2015年，[[人民行动党|人民行动党]]（PAP）宣布安宁阿敏已加入PAP，并将和四名PAP候选人参与[[2015年新加坡大选|2015年新加坡大选]]，在三巴旺集选区参选<ref>{{zh-sg}}{{cite news | author = 游桂娥 | title = “李玉云引退 王乙康与安宁阿敏加入三巴旺” | url = http://www.zaobao.com.sg/zpolitics/constituencies-battle/story20150814-514592 | publisher = [[联合早报|联合早报]] | date = 2015-08-14 | accessdate = 2017-05-16 | quote = 这个五人团队中只有马来律师安宁阿敏（36岁）属于全新的面孔，他将取代目前的三巴旺集选区议员李玉云，负责兀兰分区。 | archive-date = 2019-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191129003244/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/zpolitics/constituencies-battle/story20150814-514592 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。安宁阿敏当选后开始出任内政部政务次长<ref>{{zh-sg}}{{cite news | author = 谢诗盈 | title = “安宁阿敏：随着恐怖主义威胁加剧 警察部队应集合资源应对威胁”| url = http://www.channel8news.sg/news8/singapore/20170221-sg-saf/3537784.html | date = 2017-02-21 | accessdate = 2017-05-16 | quote = 这是一个重要的部队，战备军人和国民服役人员现在执行前线任务，在这之前，他们都是扮演支援的角色，但现在他们能到外头，和公众面对面接触，这符合年轻人要积极参与保卫国家的期望。}}</ref>。

